What you could do is have two commands, one being an alias to
noglob scp
and the other being vanilla scp
So like:

alias pcp='noglob scp'

pcp remote:foo/* .
scp * remote:foo/

Just a thought.

On 6/26/07, Richard Hartmann <richih.mailinglist@gmail.com> wrote:
